K10D0166_H0167:276b-7: dbus na'ang yod pa ma yin te //

K10D0166_H0167:276b-12: khyim khyim dag tu 'gro byed cing //
K10D0166_H0167:276b-13: chos rnams ston par mi byed do //
K10D0166_H0167:276b-14: rgyu med des pa bzang po yin //
K10D0166_H0167:276b-15: de dag sangs rgyas bslab pa rnams //

K10D0166_H0167:276b-29: mgo la spu gri sten byed cing //
K10D0166_H0167:276b-30: shing gis kha bsgyur chos gos gyon //
K10D0166_H0167:276b-31: stong pa nyid ni don med pa //

K10D0166_H0167:277a-15: 'phags pa yul 'khor skyong gis zhus pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so ////
